<span style='font-family: "Times New Roman"; font-size: 12pt; white-space: pre-wrap;'></span><span id="docs-internal-guid-019f9d7c-7fff-8626-0fc5-58a03500deb3"><br><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.44;background-color:#ffffff;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';color:#222222;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">April 16, 2020</span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.44;background-color:#ffffff;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"> </p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.44;background-color:#ffffff;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';color:#222222;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">Dear North Plainfield School Community,</span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.44;background-color:#ffffff;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"> </p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.44;background-color:#ffffff;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';color:#222222;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">I hope that this letter finds you and your loved ones well during this unprecedented and difficult time.  Since our return to school from spring recess, there are several updates I have to share with you.  </span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.44;background-color:#ffffff;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"> </p>
<ul style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;"><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';color:#222222;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.44;background-color:#ffffff;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';color:#222222;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">In an effort to prevent the further spread of Covid-19 in the State, Governor Murphy has announced that all public and private schools must remain closed through at least May 15, 2020.  The Governor will reevaluate the public health situation as it relates to schools at that time.</span></p></li></ul>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.44;margin-left: 36pt;background-color:#ffffff;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"> </p>
<ul style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;"><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';color:#222222;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.44;background-color:#ffffff;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';color:#222222;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">In partnership with Maschio’s, we have expanded feeding opportunities by opening two additional locations at East End School and West End School.  Effective Tuesday, April 21, 2020, Maschio’s will distribute lunch and the next day’s breakfast between 11:00 am and 1:00 pm at the Middle School (gym foyer), East End School (side driveway cafeteria door) and West End School (rear cafeteria door).  Social distancing guidelines must be followed for any lines, and we will mark the grounds to indicate safe distancing.</span></p></li></ul>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.44;margin-left: 36pt;background-color:#ffffff;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"> </p>
<ul style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;"><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';color:#222222;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.44;background-color:#ffffff;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';color:#222222;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">A Parent Survey will be forthcoming. Please note that due to the extension, we are organizing a committee to explore live instruction during this remote learning experience.  As more details unfold, we will share with you.</span></p></li></ul>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.44;background-color:#ffffff;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"> </p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.44;background-color:#ffffff;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';color:#222222;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">Please continue to follow the recommendations and practices outlined in social distancing and practice good hygiene.  Let us continue to take care of ourselves and each other and remember all those that we have lost during this difficult time.  I know it is hard, but I believe we will come out of this together.</span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.44;background-color:#ffffff;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"> </p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.44;background-color:#ffffff;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';color:#222222;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">Sincerely,</span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.44;background-color:#ffffff;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';color:#292b2f;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;"><span style="border:none;display:inline-block;overflow:hidden;width:141px;height:39px;"><img src="https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/dxRyl_tLKhiYdnvOa4ase6WIy-POuhqkaTrWus2qrKyf7_ejd9qA2P58DSyBG8_tXyQ3JlkZJGY-cDznInofqmp92suKVVWVDeFVvnPg2Vpqf376rPgaIoj-7_prQjj8TRezSKEE" width="141" height="39" style="margin-left:0px;margin-top:0px;"></span></span></p>
